    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this thrilling, nightmare-infused adventure, you as a puppet will harness the power of string &amp; control bar to create an engaging combat system. With an arsenal of tools and abilities designed to decimate your enemies, manipulate their action, and solve complex puzzles.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Combo system</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Take your puppeteer style combat to the next level with a fluid combo system that lets you mix and match your attacks with style. Choose from three unique control bars, each offering a different combat style to combine light but swift attack, long reaching medium attack, and bashing strike from heavy attacks into devastating combo sequences for the enemies. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collision Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Smash, crash, and slam your way through enemies and obstacles with satisfying, high-impact collisions. Customize your playstyle to take down the twisted nightmare to rescue your friend. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Wrap and Tie</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/655e7b93c5b0e2a5a8bd8ff52fb3f0a0.poster.avif?t=1771932293\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/655e7b93c5b0e2a5a8bd8ff52fb3f0a0.webm?t=1771932293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/655e7b93c5b0e2a5a8bd8ff52fb3f0a0.mp4?t=1771932293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dominate the enemies with your “puppet string”, wrap around them to pull them all into devastating crashes. Stunning them, and breaking objects as you solve puzzles and clear the path forward.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Leap</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/bbd0449e7df0185ec21f58f74d5a0088.poster.avif?t=1771932293\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/bbd0449e7df0185ec21f58f74d5a0088.webm?t=1771932293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/bbd0449e7df0185ec21f58f74d5a0088.mp4?t=1771932293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conquer the nightmare realm's irregular terrain with your trusty string and control bar. Leap over vast gaps, hop between moving platforms, and evade deadly attacks as you leap toward the end of your journey. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Slingshot</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/b83481c91d152aabb84604973fbd3bdc.poster.avif?t=1771932293\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/b83481c91d152aabb84604973fbd3bdc.webm?t=1771932293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/b83481c91d152aabb84604973fbd3bdc.mp4?t=1771932293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/d09da29cbded349a0cd8da389c8cfd7a.poster.avif?t=1771932293\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/d09da29cbded349a0cd8da389c8cfd7a.webm?t=1771932293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/d09da29cbded349a0cd8da389c8cfd7a.mp4?t=1771932293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charge up your string and launch yourself like a projectile. Carve yourself a new path by crushing a giant boulder in your way, or turn the tide of any fight with precision and speed, send them flying with crushing impacts, interrupt the boss attacks, and gain overwhelming advantage.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hook</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/a748f8a1a0b758f1debe3dbbf342efea.poster.avif?t=1771932293\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/a748f8a1a0b758f1debe3dbbf342efea.webm?t=1771932293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/a748f8a1a0b758f1debe3dbbf342efea.mp4?t=1771932293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/9a8c3875728bc008202c0aecfb507a7a.poster.avif?t=1771932293\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/9a8c3875728bc008202c0aecfb507a7a.webm?t=1771932293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/9a8c3875728bc008202c0aecfb507a7a.mp4?t=1771932293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn the environment into your ally by hooking. Pull foes into the abyss, or interrupt them to create opportunities for the perfect strike, control the battlefield with your creativity. Use the new hook and pull the ring to open a path forward in your journey.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Link</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/d3d4493cb382d23cfdad5276ef1e6511.poster.avif?t=1771932293\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/d3d4493cb382d23cfdad5276ef1e6511.webm?t=1771932293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/d3d4493cb382d23cfdad5276ef1e6511.mp4?t=1771932293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/ab32686270a5deb2e4e8dd51b9fc4564.poster.avif?t=1771932293\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/ab32686270a5deb2e4e8dd51b9fc4564.webm?t=1771932293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227900/extras/ab32686270a5deb2e4e8dd51b9fc4564.mp4?t=1771932293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Link your enemies together and take them out in one fell swoop. Deal devastating chain damage by connecting multiple foes and connect an electrical circuit to solve complex puzzles. Use this newfound power to carve through monstrous hordes and puzzle to claim your victory over every obstacle that stands in your way.</p>",
